headline: Shelf-Stable Food Stocks Q3 Teardown: Post (NYSE:POST) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q3, starting with Post (NYSE:POST).
